title: Jay Pharoah And Adam Pally: Licensed To 'Champaign ILL'
description: Saturday Night Live alum Jay Pharoah looks back on his early stand-up days and shows off his celebrity impressions in a game with his co-star on the comedy series Champaign ILL, actor Adam Pally. Plus, a music parody game that will pump you up!
